These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: folk, rock, dubstep, electronic, metal, salsa, jazz
1. the fan of salsa is on the right of the fan of rock##1
2. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
3. the fan of jazz is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
4. the fan of metal is between the fan of folk and the fan of dubstep##2
5. the fan of electronic is between the fan of rock and the fan of folk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3   |    4    |  5  |   6   |   7   |
| Music-Genre   | jazz | dubstep | metal | folk | electronic | rock | salsa |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-2::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: drawing, magic-tricks, board-games, rock-climbing, writing, traveling, photography
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
4. the person who's hobby is board-games is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |   3    |   4   |     5      |    6    |     7      |
| Hobby   | traveling | photography | drawing | board-games | rock-climbing | magic-tricks | writing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-3::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: skydiving, chess, rock-climbing, video-games, gardening, camping, reading
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
5. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
6. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is chess##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4      |   5    |    6    |   7    |
| Hobby   | reading | camping | gardening | chess | skydiving | rock-climbing | video-games |

